{"tid":1150904,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔撚該你班肥閪有返少少自覺","createTime":"2019-05-12T07:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T12:53:29.000Z","uid":45173,"like":159,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5c7ac4b9b2523231efa5ce46c3ae960a032eed6f","tid":1150904,"uid":45173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"一上車就行入去，咪撚企係門口ok？<br />\n好撚臭呀屌你老母！掂撚到你後背d肥膏呀屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n件衫透晒d汗出黎，望撚到你都熱呀！<br />\n成車酸縮味，仲唔係你條肥婆散發出黎既？<br />\n仲要同d大肚婆爭位，真係好撚嘔心呀！<br />\n<br />\n依家氣溫係28度，過多排就30度以上啦！<br />\n60kg以上，自己檢討下啦！<br />\n咪話本龜頭唔體諒你地，60kg已經係少少肥<br />\n但仲可以接受，通常都唔會肥到d肉必晒出黎<br />\n而過左60，又唔係170cm高果班 你地好自為之<br />\n<br />\n唔好再臭撚親我！！！！！好撚憎夏天呀！！屌！！"},{"pid":"99fcb4327b4050194e544f54b5c645e7127bc4b3","tid":1150904,"uid":109136,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"幾時又出故屌鳩肥婆 ?"},{"pid":"cfcffc153e4a5b0046a6402b4129b28aa6f538da","tid":1150904,"uid":45173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:52:35.000Z","msg":"屌！！"},{"pid":"276584e07314d580f294c4d4ab5baf53c60f10b2","tid":1150904,"uid":38907,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"喺商場都聞到陣酸臭味"},{"pid":"0a2d716662dc3d62927a582f369725727fe0dc8a","tid":1150904,"uid":177152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:52:52.000Z","msg":"你的長長來了"},{"pid":"9752a04c1cab899c274315cd6c4e6363311e85ef","tid":1150904,"uid":2920,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fatcmoji/fat003.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fatcmoji/fat003.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fatcmoji/fat003.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隔住個茫都有陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f839d1810d6111471e99ef7248fc8ce9fd5cc4a8","tid":1150904,"uid":45173,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"99fcb4327b4050194e544f54b5c645e7127bc4b3